# Terraform local state (must never be committed)
**/.terraform/
**/terraform.tfstate
**/terraform.tfstate.*
**/.terraform.tfstate.lock.info
**/crash.log
**/crash.*.log

# Sensitive tfvars (optional: keep them out of git)
# Note: terraform.tfvars is allowed as it contains non-sensitive defaults
**/*.tfvars
!terraform.tfvars
**/*.tfvars.json

# Terraform CLI plans
**/*.tfplan
**/*.plan

# Override files (rare, but can contain local overrides)
**/*_override.tf
**/*_override.tf.json
**/override.tf
**/override.tf.json
